title: Highway Thru Hell S05E03 Bridge Out 720p HDTV x264
description:
Bridge Out

A semi-trailer jackknifes on a narrow canyon bridge, the driver narrowly escaping plunging to his death. Jamie and his Heavy Rescue team are then tasked with pulling the pinned semi-trailer free on a slippery fuel coated bridge. On an active logging road in B.C.'s Fraser Valley, the Mission Towing team races to finish a recovery of a truck that rolled 100 feet down an embankment.
